Even doing something as simple as reading the study and results data properly - analysing, not believing without applying critical thinking - and the PILs is illuminating.Also, please look at the newer figures coming through, which alarmingly show Covid deaths are now happening within weeks of vaccination. In Iowa, for example, 100% of their recent Covid deaths had had their jabs around 2 weeks prior. There are many examples of such incidents. I can safely predict that all the ongoing and forthcominb Covid deaths will be attributed to another new variant (all coronaviruses continuously mutate) rather than to the immune-response damage caused by these ‰ÛÏvaccines‰Û. Look at the study referred to by Kennedy, in which the animal subjects appeared to respond well to their vaccine, but had an exaggerated response when confronted with the virus in the wild, and died.I can pretty much guarantee that next autumn and winter will see higher than normal deaths because of this. Did you know there are concerns over blood donation where the donor has been vaccinated? Have you actually seen any of the information re: fertility being adversely affected by these jabs? Given that a) no-one has so far identified the virus, and b) it‰Ûªs a coronavirus (same family as the common cold, so constantly mutating hence no-one has ever found a cure in the preceding 70 years of research, how can they possibly have created an effective and safe vax in 2020? Answer is, they haven‰Ûªt. The Safety & Efficacy Trials don‰Ûªt finish until Jan 2022 for Pfizer, this Oct for Moderna. So, not to put too fine a point on it, anyone who has these jabs is participating in the trials without realising it.
